# ASM Enterprise — Attack Surface Management Script

**Based on:** Enterprise Financial Services ASM SOP v1.0  
**Language:** Python 3.9+  
**Platform:** Kali Linux (recommended), Ubuntu 22.04+

> **FOR AUTHORIZED SECURITY ASSESSMENTS ONLY.**  
> Ensure written authorization from an appropriate executive before running any active phases.  
> Unauthorized scanning may violate the Computer Fraud and Abuse Act (CFAA) and equivalent laws.

